data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET, NO FAULT OF SELLER. You will feel right at home in this Beautiful Columbine floorplan located in Southern California's Premier 55+ Community of Sun Lakes. The kitchen has plenty of space to entertain many or just a few. Light counter tops with oak cabinets make this kitchen one you will spend time in. The master bedroom is large with a nice sized Walk-in closet and the guest bedroom has its own bathroom next to it. Need some quiet time to read? There is a nice office/den/sitting room for that. Make yourself at home lounging on your covered patio. Come check out what all sun Lakes has to offer. Golf, swimming, pickleball, bocce ball, shows, comedy nights, full-service restaurant, and more. You' re also just 30-minute drive to Beautiful Palm Springs, shopping and casinos.
